Package DeliveryManSystem

Class DeliveryMan

  • java.lang.Object
    • DeliveryManSystem.DeliveryMan
  • public class DeliveryMan
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the delivery man, there are methods to send the credentials to the pickup point and methods that return the deliveries to do and those expired.
